text: Wanda Piątkowska (born 23 June 1960) is a Polish rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1980 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1980 Summer Olympics Category:People from Grudziądz
